lgp.core.evolution.fitness

Class MultipleOutputFitnessContext<TData>

  • FitnessContext
    • lgp.core.evolution.fitness.MultipleOutputFitnessContext<TData>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Module

    public class MultipleOutputFitnessContext<TData>
extends FitnessContext

    Facilitates fitness evaluation for programs which have multiple outputs.

    For programs with a single output, class SingleOutputFitnessContext should be used.

    See Also:
    class SingleOutputFitnessContext
